theme_override_font_sizes/bold_font_size = 35
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "
[b]Overview[/b]
This is a 4-player strategy board game set in a wildlife conservation scenario.
Each player takes on a unique role and competes to be the first to fulfil their role's win condition by playing cards and shaping the board.

[b]The Board [/b]
The board is a grid of tiles, each one of three types:

	[b]Forest[/b] 											[b]Plantation[/b] 									[b]Human Dominated Area[/b]
	natural habitat	 							agricultural land							populated areas









[b]Game Pieces[/b]

	[b]Elephants [/b]										[b]Villager[/b]







There can only be 1 elephant per tile or 2 villagers per tile Villagers
"
fit_content = true

