text = "[b]Setup[/b]
The Player will first choose a scenario from the senario selection screen.














Then each player has to chose a unique role from role scenario.
In the Role scenario, the player will be allowed to configure how many bots they want to play with, the bot's speed and difficulty.














Each player will have 5 cards on hand at the start.
"
fit_content = true

