bbcode_enabled = true
text = "
[b]Action Card[/b]
1. On your turn play a card from your hand.
2. Follow any on-screen prompts. 
3. Press end turn to pass to the next player.
4. If you didn't choose a card before the time runs out, your turn automatically ends.

	[b]Colour	Theme[/b]

			[b]Green[/b] 
			Protects the environment or provide a way for both humans and elephants to coexist.

			[b]Yellow[/b]
			Neutral actions that reduce the human-elephant conflict, but creates risks for both elephants or humans.

			[b]Red	[/b] 
			 Harmful action that directly harm elephants, humans or the environment.

			[b]Black[/b]
			Special action cards that must be played if it is on your hand.


[b]Winning [/b]
The first player to meet all of their role's win conditions simultaneously wins.

"
fit_content = true

